{"tid":1534033,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我在此警告所有香港人 及中共領導人","createTime":"2019-09-03T01:28:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T03:30:29.000Z","uid":167938,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d561e68163946776e9bd26d78c505dc5a12697f3","tid":1534033,"uid":167938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T01:28:58.000Z","msg":"香港問題必須藉由<br />\n答應<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求</span></span><br />\n而解決<br />\n<br />\n中共領導人 企圖以 少數人如林鄭祭旗<br />\n藉以解決香港問題是極為幼稚<br />\n<br />\n香港人<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">絕不妥協</span></span><br />\n<br />\n五大訴求 如不落實<br />\n<br />\n香港人將奮力戰至 中國，香港 全面攬炒<br />\n以推翻政府為目標<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一直奮戰至死為止</span><br />\n同時間黑警暴行必須追究到底<br />\n<br />\nIdea is bulletproof<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 <br />\n時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"6088a04403bac0a3d88aaaf04b39b90a918d1fd8","tid":1534033,"uid":266362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T01:29:33.000Z","msg":"跪求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">想大個仔獨立必睇</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">召喚攬炒巴及歷史法師！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n請幫推以下post！<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">香港人一定要知！</span></span></span>遇怪魔想變大個，就一定一定要睇！<br />\n<br />\n［召喚攬炒巴] 星球級反擊！香港最後本錢 VS 赤獸<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1529054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https:/